name: Real BB
description:
A model optimized to display realistic females with huge boobs.

This model is a general purpose model, therefore it can create a wide range of images. It tends to make women rather beautiful, naked and with big boobs though.

This model has not been trained but is an assembly from various other models. Too many have gone into it to name, but big thanks go out to the amazing F222, Hassan Blend, KriboMix and of course the basis for it all: hyperbreasts.

Version 2+ needs a VAE installed, like https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/sd-vae-ft-mse-original

Version 3 has a safetensor version, because people keep asking.

This model is not trigger based, however the model seems to react to the word "implants" by making the boobs much bigger than without.
